## ğŸš€ How to Use (3 Steps)

### Step 1: Clone This Branch

```bash
git clone -b reel-02-beamgrid https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/animated-lab.git
cd animated-lab
```

### Step 2: Install & Run

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Step 3: Open Browser

Go to: `http://localhost:3000`

**That's it!** ğŸ‰ You should see the animated grid.

