## âš™ï¸ Customization Options

| Option | What it does | Example |
|--------|--------------|---------|
| `beamColor` | Beam color (light mode) | `"rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.8)"` |
| `darkBeamColor` | Beam color (dark mode) | `"rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8)"` |
| `beamCount` | Number of beams | `12` (default: 8) |
| `beamSpeed` | How fast beams move | `0.15` (default: 0.1) |
| `glowIntensity` | How much glow | `80` (default: 50) |
| `interactive` | Mouse tracking on/off | `true` or `false` |

### Example with options:
```jsx
<BeamGridBackground
  beamColor="rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.6)"
  beamCount={15}
  beamSpeed={0.15}
  glowIntensity={80}
/>
```


